## Verification checklist

- Every changed file is in the PRD-owned folder.
- Dependencies follow `UI -> GameStateManager -> logic -> catalogs/resources/constants`.
- Logic does not depend on the facade or UI.
- Runtime player state remains Dictionary-based.
- Canonical filenames and paths match the PRD exactly.
- Dictionary keys, IDs, classes, and constants follow their documented naming convention.
- GDScript project references use `res://`.
- No `systems/`, root `resources/`, or `PhaseCoordinator` legacy pattern was introduced.
